### Backend and Database

- Use Supabase for backend services, including authentication and database interactions.
- Follow Supabase guidelines for security and performance.
- Use freezed and json_serializable for defining immutable DTO models and validating backend data.
- Use supabase from Supabase.instance.client in Dart routes instead of importing supabaseClient directly
